Publish articles

Usage: mf publish [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  run     Publish article to a target (supported: local, yuque-prompt)
  update  Update a publish_records entry in mind-index.yaml

Options:
      --root <PATH>      Mind Repo root directory
      --config <PATH>    Config file path
  -v, --verbose...       Verbose output
  -q, --quiet            Silence non-error output
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color         Disable colored output
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
